{
  "info": {
    "name": "Knowledge Platform - Stage 6 热搜榜单测试",
    "description": "# 知识库与内容发布平台 - Stage 6 热搜榜单专项测试\n\n## 测试范围\n- 热搜 Top 10 公开访问\n- 阅读热度 (+1) + 5分钟去重\n- 点赞热度 (+3) + 永久去重\n- 评论热度 (+1)\n- 多级缓存验证 (Caffeine L1 → Redis ZSET L2 → MySQL L3)\n- 热度分数验证\n- 边界情况\n\n## 环境变量说明\n| 变量 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|------|\n| `baseUrl` | `http://localhost:8080` | 网关地址 |\n| `token` | (自动填充) | 用户 JWT 令牌 |\n| `userId` | (自动填充) | 当前用户 ID |\n| `trendingArticleId` | (自动填充) | 用于热度测试的文章 ID |\n\n## 测试流程\n1. **准备阶段**: 注册 → 登录 → 创建并发布文章\n2. **基础功能**: 查询热搜榜（公开访问）\n3. **阅读热度**: 多次阅读同一文章，验证防重\n4. **点赞热度**: 点赞文章，验证热度 +3\n5. **评论热度**: 评论文章，验证热度 +1\n6. **总分验证**: 验证 total = 阅读(+1) + 点赞(+3) + 评论(+1)\n7. **缓存验证**: 连续快速请求，观察缓存命中\n8. **边界测试**: 无认证访问、空榜单等\n\n## 快速开始\n1. 导入此 Collection 到 Postman\n2. 创建 Environment，设置 `baseUrl` = `http://localhost:8080`\n3. 按文件夹顺序执行：`0-准备` → `1-基础` → `2-阅读热度` → `3-点赞热度` → `4-评论热度` → `5-总分验证` → `6-边界测试`\n4. 或直接运行 `7-一键测试` 文件夹（Run Collection）",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "knowledge-platform-stage6"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0-准备阶段 (Setup)",
      "description": "创建测试用户、登录、创建并发布一篇文章，为后续热度测试准备数据",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "S0-1: 注册测试用户",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    console.log('用户注册成功:', pm.response.json().data.username);",
                  "}",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 400) {",
                  "    console.log('用户已存在，跳过注册');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('注册成功或用户已存在', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect([200, 400]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"trending_tester\",\n    \"password\": \"trending123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "register"]
            },
            "description": "注册一个专用测试用户，用于后续所有热度操作"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "S0-2: 登录获取 Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', json.data.userId);",
                  "    console.log('Token 已保存, userId=' + json.data.userId);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('登录成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.have.property('token');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"username\": \"trending_tester\",\n    \"password\": \"trending123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/user/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "user", "login"]
            },
            "description": "登录并自动保存 token 到环境变量"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "S0-3: 创建文章(草稿)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('trendingArticleId', json.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('文章已创建, id=' + json.data.id);",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('文章创建成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data).to.have.property('id');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"title\": \"Stage6 热搜测试文章\",\n    \"content\": \"这是一篇用于测试热搜榜单功能的文章。阅读、点赞、评论都会增加热度分。\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles"]
            },
            "description": "创建一篇草稿文章，articleId 自动保存到环境变量"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "S0-4: 发布文章",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('文章发布成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().data.status).to.eql('PUBLISHED');",
                  "    console.log('文章已发布');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{trendingArticleId}}/publish",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{trendingArticleId}}", "publish"]
            },
            "description": "发布文章 — 发布后的文章才会出现在热搜榜单中"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1-基础功能 (Basic)",
      "description": "热搜榜基础查询功能验证",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T1-1: 查询热搜榜(公开访问，无 Token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('状态码 200 — 无需认证即可访问', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('返回 Result<T> 标准格式', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('message');",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('data');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('data 为数组类型', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('数组长度 <= 10', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data.length).to.be.at.most(10);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (json.data.length > 0) {",
                  "    var first = json.data[0];",
                  "    pm.test('每条记录包含必要字段: id, title, authorId, likeCount, heatScore', function() {",
                  "        pm.expect(first).to.have.property('id');",
                  "        pm.expect(first).to.have.property('title');",
                  "        pm.expect(first).to.have.property('authorId');",
                  "        pm.expect(first).to.have.property('likeCount');",
                  "        pm.expect(first).to.have.property('heatScore');",
                  "        pm.expect(first.heatScore).to.be.a('number');",
                  "    });",
                  "    ",
                  "    console.log('热搜榜共 ' + json.data.length + ' 条:');",
                  "    json.data.forEach(function(item, i) {",
                  "        console.log('  ' + (i+1) + '. [' + item.id + '] ' + item.title + ' (热度: ' + item.heatScore + ', 点赞: ' + item.likeCount + ')');",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('热搜榜当前为空 — 执行后续阅读/点赞/评论步骤后将有数据');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "trending"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n验证热搜榜作为公开接口可被任意访问，不携带 Authorization 头\n\n### 预期结果\n- HTTP 200\n- data 为数组，长度 ≤ 10\n- 每条记录含 id, title, authorId, likeCount, heatScore\n- 按 heatScore 降序排列"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T1-2: 查询热搜榜(带 Token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('认证用户同样可访问', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('返回数据一致', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "trending"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n验证携带 Token 的认证用户同样可访问（不因鉴权逻辑被拦截）\n\n### 预期结果\n- 与 T1-1 返回相同数据"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T1-3: 初始榜单(空或含旧数据)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('初始热搜榜: ' + json.data.length + ' 条');",
                  "",
                  "// 如果是新 Redis，榜单应为空或仅含之前测试的留数据",
                  "// 记录当前状态供后续对比",
                  "if (json.data.length > 0) {",
                  "    var foundOurArticle = json.data.find(function(item) {",
                  "        return item.id == pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId');",
                  "    });",
                  "    if (foundOurArticle) {",
                  "        console.log('测试文章已上榜，当前热度: ' + foundOurArticle.heatScore);",
                  "        pm.environment.set('baselineHeatScore', foundOurArticle.heatScore);",
                  "    } else {",
                  "        console.log('测试文章尚未上榜（热度分为0或不存在）');",
                  "        pm.environment.set('baselineHeatScore', 0);",
                  "    }",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('baselineHeatScore', 0);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "trending"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n获取基线热度分，供后续步骤对比验证\n\n### 说明\n将测试文章的当前热度分记录为 baselineHeatScore，后续每步操作后对比增量"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2-阅读热度 (Read Heat +1)",
      "description": "验证阅读文章触发热度 +1，以及 5 分钟内重复阅读去重",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T2-1: 首次阅读 — 热度应 +1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('文章详情获取成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('第1次阅读文章, id=' + pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{trendingArticleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{trendingArticleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n首次阅读文章，触发 ZINCRBY hot_articles +1\n\n### 预期结果\n- HTTP 200 返回文章详情\n- article-service 日志输出: `Hot article read recorded: articleId=X, score +1`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T2-2: 5分钟内重复阅读 — 不应增加热度",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('重复阅读仍返回文章详情', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('第2次阅读(应立即请求，验证去重)...');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{trendingArticleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{trendingArticleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n同一用户在 5 分钟内重复阅读同一文章，由于 Redis 去重 key `read:article:{id}:user:{uid}` 仍有效，不应再次增加热度\n\n### 预期结果\n- 日志中不再输出 `score +1`（去重生效）\n- 或查看 Redis: `ZSCORE hot_articles {id}` 与之前相同"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T2-3: 验证阅读后热度变化",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "console.log('阅读后热搜榜:');",
                  "",
                  "var baseline = parseFloat(pm.environment.get('baselineHeatScore') || 0);",
                  "",
                  "var ourArticle = json.data.find(function(item) {",
                  "    return item.id == pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (ourArticle) {",
                  "    var currentHeat = ourArticle.heatScore;",
                  "    console.log('测试文章当前热度: ' + currentHeat + ' (基线: ' + baseline + ')');",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.test('阅读后热度大于等于基线(含+1)', function() {",
                  "        pm.expect(currentHeat).to.be.at.least(baseline + 0.5);",
                  "    });",
                  "",
                  "    pm.environment.set('heatAfterRead', currentHeat);",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('文章未上榜(热度分可能为0，需先有互动)');",
                  "    pm.environment.set('heatAfterRead', 0);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "trending"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n确认阅读后热搜榜中的热度分已增加\n\n### 预期结果\n- 测试文章的 heatScore 比基线高（增加约 1 分）"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3-点赞热度 (Like Heat +3)",
      "description": "验证点赞触发热度 +3，以及永久去重",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T3-1: 首次点赞 — 热度应 +3",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('点赞成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('点赞成功, articleId=' + pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{trendingArticleId}}/like",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{trendingArticleId}}", "like"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n首次点赞文章，触发 ZINCRBY hot_articles +3\n\n### 预期结果\n- HTTP 200\n- article-service 日志: `Hot article like recorded: articleId=X, score +3`\n- interact-service 日志: `Like recorded: articleId=X, userId=X, heat +3`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T3-2: 重复点赞 — 应返回错误",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('重复点赞返回错误', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(400);",
                  "});",
                  "pm.test('错误消息提示已点赞', function() {",
                  "    var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.message).to.include('已点赞');",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('防重生效: 重复点赞被拒绝');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}"}
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/articles/{{trendingArticleId}}/like",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "articles", "{{trendingArticleId}}", "like"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n验证点赞防重机制 — 同一用户对同一文章仅可点赞一次\n\n### 预期结果\n- HTTP 400\n- message: \"您已点赞过该文章\""
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "T3-3: 验证点赞后热度变化",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "var heatAfterRead = parseFloat(pm.environment.get('heatAfterRead') || 0);",
                  "",
                  "var ourArticle = json.data.find(function(item) {",
                  "    return item.id == pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "if (ourArticle) {",
                  "    console.log('热度变化: ' + heatAfterRead + ' → ' + ourArticle.heatScore);",
                  "",
                  "    pm.test('点赞后热度 >= 阅读后热度 + 2.5(≈+3)', function() {",
                  "        pm.expect(ourArticle.heatScore).to.be.at.least(heatAfterRead + 2.5);",
                  "    });",
                  "    ",
                  "    pm.environment.set('heatAfterLike', ourArticle.heatScore);",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.log('文章未上榜');",
                  "    pm.environment.set('heatAfterLike', heatAfterRead + 3);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trending",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "trending"]
            },
            "description": "### 测试目标\n确认点赞后热度分比阅读后增加约 3\n\n### 预期结果\n- heatScore 约增加 3"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4-评论热度 (Comment Heat +1)",
      "description": "验证评论触发热度 +1",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "T4-1: 发表评论 — 热度应 +1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('评论提交成功', function() {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.eql(200);",
                  "});",
                  "console.log('评论成功, articleId=' + pm.environment.get('trendingArticleId'));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
